sections.content:
Question:
In what format are the free AI applications provided?
Will the AI-Model be provided, or will it be provided in a trained state?
Also, will the AI application be provided in source code or binary form?
Answer:
Free AI Applications provides the source code, pre-build application binary and pre-trained AI model objects, which allow you to select the application from various use cases, and run it on the board immediately.
Suitable Products
RZ/V
